# Nachos

> Just a single layer to make sure every bite is perfect. #texmex #app

Preheat the oven to 350 degrees.

- Chips | Tortilla, 1 bag | 
- Mexican Cheese | 4 cheese, 2 cups, shredded | 

Layer the chips on a cookie sheet lined with a silpat and sprinkle with 2 cups of cheese. Cook for about 4 minutes until the cheese is barely melted.

- Chili | 1 cup | 
- Mexican Cheese | Creamy, 2 cups, shredded | 

Remove from oven, evenly spoon on the chili, cover with the remaining cheese, and return to the oven for about 5 more minutes.

- Cilantro | 1/4 cup | Chopped
- Green Onion | 1/4 cup | Chopped
- Sour Cream |  | 
- Salsa |  | 

Remove from the oven, plate up, and sprinkle on cilantro and green onion. Serve with sour cream and salsa.
